original_title: What Makes This Song Stink Ep. 4 - “Hey Soul Sister: The Movie” featuring Dr. Fog
overview: Pat Finnerty explores what makes the song, Hey Soul Sister by Train, stink while also trying to ensure that his video covering Beverly Hills by Weezer does not become his Pinkerton.
